title: VA - Slap On That Great 70's B Side [3 CDs] Rock N Pop 1971- 76
description:
Just some of those brilliant tracks that adorned the flip sides of some of the top singles from the early to mid Seventies.  They weren&#039;t throw away songs, far from it!  In some cases they were just as good, if not better than the A side.  Often they were more representative of the artist than the bit hit that was stealin&#039; all the limelight.  Here are some real, flippin&#039; gems.
